{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_09_03",
  "title": "白石千紗 3話 思い出してくれるように",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――打ち合わせからしばらく経ち",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Some time after the meeting",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1433.3333333,
          "startTime": 1.4333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2066.6666667000004,
          "startTime": 2.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 1.4333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "お疲れ様です、{user}さん\n届いた衣装って……もしかしてこれですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you for your hard work‚ {user}-san.\nThe delivered costume… could it be this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.7333334605
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "わぁっ……綺麗……\nとっても魅力的な衣装になりましたね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow… it's beautiful…\nIt's become such an attractive costume!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "デザインを考えてくれた千紗に一番に\n見せたくてな。届いてすぐに連絡させてもらった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wanted to show it first to Chisa‚ who designed it.\nSo I contacted you right after it arrived.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.8666667938
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "ありがとうございます！　わぁ……スカートの裾が\n星見の海の波みたいで素敵……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thank you! Wow… the hem of the skirt looks like the waves\nof Hoshimi's ocean‚ so lovely…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "千紗のイメージ通りに仕上がってるか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Did it turn out like you imagined?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.0666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 33.7333334605
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "イメージ以上です！　悩みましたけど\nやっぱりこの生地にして良かったです……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's even better than I imagined! I was torn‚ but\nI'm glad I chose this fabric after all…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "凄いなぁ……私もいつか、自分の手で\nこんな衣装を作ってみたいなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's amazing… someday I'd like to make\na costume like this with my own hands…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3248505592,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.2333334605
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、デザイン会社から千紗にプレゼントが\nあるみたいだぞ。そこの箱を確認してみるといい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ it seems the design company has\na present for you. Check that box over there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "これは……衣装と同じ生地、ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This is… the same fabric as the costume?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.6666667938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 55.6666667938
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 61.0333334605
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "衣装を作る時に余ったらしくてな\n自由に使って下さいと一緒に送られてきたよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Apparently it was left over when making the costume.\nThey included a note― \"Please feel free to use it.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 67.666669337
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……量はそこまで多くないですし\n使えるとしたら小物ぐらいでしょうか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… there's not that much of it.\nSo if I were to use it‚ maybe small accessories…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.3333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "ライブに向けてみんなへのプレゼントを作れたら\n素敵かもしれません……うーん……あっ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I could make presents for everyone for the live\nit might be nice… hmm… oh!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.1666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.6333360036
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "シュシュならこの生地の量でもみんなの分を\n作ることが出来るかもしれません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With scrunchies‚ I might be able to make enough for everyone\nwith this amount of fabric.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.0000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "シュシュか\n普段使い出来るいいプレゼントになりそうだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see‚ scrunchies.\nThat sounds like a nice present they can use regularly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 92.6333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.866669337
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくですし水族館らしいデザインにしたいですよね\nそれぞれ、お魚のイラストがあると楽しいかも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since we have the chance‚ I'd like to make them aquarium-themed.\nIt might be fun if each one has a different fish illustration…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.7666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "俺も手伝おうか？\nとはいっても、作り方は知らないんだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you need my hand?\nI don't know how to make them‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 111.4333349864
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、私が教えてあげます！\n一緒に素敵なシュシュを作りましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then I'll teach you!\nLet's make lovely scrunchies together!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.1333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ当日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Live Performance Day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.3533349673,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.7666692098
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.8666692098
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "どうですか、{user}さん？\n衣装、似合っているでしょうか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How do I look‚ {user}-san?\nDoes the costume suit me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.0000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "とても似合っているよ。完璧に着こなせてる\n自分でデザインしただけはあるな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It suits you very well. You're wearing it perfectly.\nYou really did design it yourself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.3000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 134.9000082652
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……そう言ってもらえると嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe… I'm happy to hear you say that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.9000082652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.9333415985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "作ったシュシュもみんなにプレゼント出来ましたし\n後はライブを成功させるだけですね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was able to give everyone the scrunchies I made too.\nSo now all that's left is to make the live a success!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.3666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "今日はいつも以上に気合いが入ってるみたいだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem more fired up than usual today.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.9666749318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 150.2333415985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "なんてったって里帰りライブですから！\n成長した私達をみんなに見てもらいたいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's a homecoming live after all!\nI want everyone to see how much we've grown.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.0000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 158.1333415985
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "そのためにレッスンも頑張ってきましたし\n気合いも十分です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've worked hard in lessons for this\nand I'm fully motivated!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.9333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "デビューしたばかりの頃の私とは違います\n今日のライブは任せておいて下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm different from when I just debuted.\nYou can leave today's live to me!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.3000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "本当に頼もしくなったな、千紗……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've really become reliable‚ Chisa…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.5000082652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 170.5000082652
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "では、そろそろ時間なので行ってきますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ it's almost time so I'll be going!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.8333415985,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2799.9942780000138,
          "startTime": 176.6333358765
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 176.0666692098
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "お、おい、そっちはステージとは真逆だぞ\nアイドル用の入り口はこっちだ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-hey‚ that's the complete opposite direction from the stage.\nThe idol entrance is this way!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.8333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 183.1000082652
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "あ、あれっ！？　ご、ごめんなさい！\n私、見間違っちゃったみたいで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ oops!? S-sorry!\nI seem to have mistaken the direction…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.2000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 189.5000082652
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "はは。まだまだ千紗も目が離せないな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haha. I still can't take my eyes off you‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 189.5000082652,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 166.6609446000109,
          "startTime": 189.6666692098
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs020.m4a",
      "text": "も、もう！　そんなことないです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no! That's not true!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.1000082652,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 197.8000082652
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_stagesleeves-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "stagesleeves-00-noon",
      "startTime": 203.2666692098
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs021.m4a",
      "text": "そ、それでは、気を取り直して行ってきます\nミスしないように、ミスしないように……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-well then‚ I'll pull myself together and go.\nDon't make mistakes‚ don't make mistakes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.2666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_seaparaaquastadium-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3",
      "startTime": 208.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs022.m4a",
      "text": "この街でいろんな思い出を作ってきました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've made so many memories in this city.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 209.8333212535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs023.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロのみんなと切磋琢磨したり\nファンの方々と一緒にライブを盛り上げたり……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Competing and improving with everyone at Hoshimi Pro\nand hyping up the live shows together with the fans…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 217.4666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs024.m4a",
      "text": "私が今こうしてアイドルを続けられているのは\n星見市での経験のおかげです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason I can continue being an idol like this now\nis thanks to my experiences in Hoshimi City.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.7333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs025.m4a",
      "text": "（一つ一つの思い出を私は忘れたくない）\n（みんなにも、ずっと覚えていてもらいたい）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I don't want to forget each and every memory）\n（I want everyone to remember them forever too.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 234.9333358765,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs026.m4a",
      "text": "（だから、この場にいる全員がこの瞬間を）\n（ずっと忘れないように、最高のライブをします）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（So I want everyone here to）\n（never forget this moment‚ so I'll give the best live.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.6666692098,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs027.m4a",
      "text": "（星見市の海を見た時に、この衣装を着た私達の）\n（ライブを、ふと思い出してくれるように――）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（When they see Hoshimi City's ocean‚ I hope they'll）\n（suddenly remember our live in these costumes――）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 252.9000025432,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_03-chs028.m4a",
      "text": "星見市のみなさん、ただいま～！\n成長した私達のライブ、楽しんでいって下さい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone in Hoshimi City‚ I'm home~!\nPlease enjoy our live performance showing how much we've grown!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 260.9000025432,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 2500.0471751999953,
          "startTime": 259.6000025432
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
